  "title": "Banking: Credit Administration (Assistant Manager/AVP)",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>*Seeking for a Credit Admin who has minimum of 5 years of credit admin/loans experience from the Banking industry*</strong></em></p><p><strong>THE COMPANY</strong></p><p>Rooted in their commitment and service to their clients, the company has a well-received yet stable brand within the Banking sector. They currently seek a Credit Administration (Admin) Assistant Manager/AVP to be part of their Credit documentation team.</p><p><strong>JOB RESPONSIBILITIES</strong></p><ul><li>Perform credit administration and credit related duties</li><li>Assist with clients onboarding matters</li><li>Check that loan agreements are coherent with agreed terms</li><li>Perform data input for credit facilities</li><li>Perform CDD for new and existing clients</li><li>Work closely with other business stakeholders</li></ul><p><strong>JOB REQUIREMENTS</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/LCCI/CAT or Degree in Business Studies/Finance/Banking/Economics/Commerce or any other relevant education</li><li>Minimum 5 years of Credit Administration (Admin)/Loan Operations- dealing with loan agreements experience in Banking industry</li><li>Meticulous, organized, team player and has good interpersonal skills</li></ul><p>If you will like to explore this opportunity, please email your resume in Microsoft Word format to <a href=\"mailto:marie@resolutehunter.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">marie@resolutehunter.com</a></p><p>We thank you for your interest and will contact shortlisted candidates for more detailed discussion.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please refer to our website https://resolutehunter.com/</p><p>EA Licence 18C9105</p><p>EA Reg R1105305</p>",
